# DefaultSettingsLinkLabel

**Structure**

The default label to use for a settings link.

## Declaration

```swift
struct DefaultSettingsLinkLabel
```

## Overview

You don’t use this type directly. Instead, the system creates it automatically when you construct a [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/SettingsLink] with the default label.
